text: The Texas Stars are an American professional ice hockey team that began playing in 2009. They currently play in the American Hockey League and are the farm team of the Dallas Stars of the NHL. They play their home games in Cedar Park, Texas at the Cedar Park Center. Their ECHL affiliate team is the Idaho Steelheads and their CHL affiliate team is the Allen Americans. ==Other websites== *Texas Stars Official Site Category:American Hockey League teams Category:Dallas Stars Category:Ice hockey teams in the United States Category:2009 establishments in the United States Category:2000s establishments in Texas
